I"Ù<p>GitHub can be used for personal site and blog.</p>

<p>It can further be used to project sites. This is kind of a sub-site/sub-domain of main site.</p>

<p>My site:
<code class="highlighter-rouge">myname.github.io/</code></p>

<p>Project Site:
<code class="highlighter-rouge">myname.github.io/abc_project/</code></p>

<p>All projects repository come under <strong>gh-pages</strong> branch and not master.</p>

<p>Creating a sub site is same as creating a main site.</p>
